lead_paragraph: Dak Prescott and Ezekiel Elliott each accounted for two touchdowns as Dallas extended its regular-season record for consecutive victories. In other games, the Lions edged the Vikings, and the Steelers blasted the Colts.

headline.print_headline: Cowboys Win 10th in Row; Lions Take Division Lead
headline.main: Dallas Cowboys Top Washington Redskins for Their 10th Straight Win

snippet: Dak Prescott and Ezekiel Elliott each accounted for two touchdowns as Dallas extended its regular-season record for consecutive victories. In other games, the Lions edged the Vikings, and the Steelers blasted the Colts....
abstract: Dallas Cowboys defeat Washington Redskins, 31-26, extending regular-season record to 10 straight wins; other Football scores noted.
